name: Funny Selfie # 2
description:
'Funny Selfie' is a PFP collection project in TXZ. No Road Map, No Discord, just funny faces with huge eyes and mouths 😍. We will grow little by little, so there is some scarcity and exclusivity here 😁. If you're looking for a fun PFP that represents your spirit and that doesn't cost a fortune, you can take one ❤️. 1/1 ED.

Selfies rule the world 💪🏼. Enjoy!
